  "title": "Land Surveyor",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Attend daily subcontractor meetings and carry out required survey setting-out lines/points for structural and architectural works.</li>\n  <li>Maintain close communication with project staff and subcontractors to understand requirements, plan effectively, and ensure timelines are met.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accuracy in all survey setting-out lines/points, handing over work properly to other parties to minimize site errors.</li>\n  <li>Follow a disciplined routine in general setting-out works according to floor framing plans, including checking formwork levels before and after casting, and verifying as-built slab levels, wall verticality, and column alignment.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate confidence in survey work through repeated checks and ensure all survey tasks are closed out daily to eliminate potential errors.</li>\n  <li>Arrange timely calibration and servicing of surveying instruments, maintaining records for audits by government agencies or internal SOP requirements.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with Licensed Land Surveyors to ensure proper AMSL and As-Built Surveys are conducted, with endorsed submissions to the authorities.</li>\n  <li>Support the Environmental Health &amp; Safety program established by the Project Manager and WSHO to maintain a safe and clean site.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
